00:53:37.960 --> 00:53:40.420
Gottfried Herold: I think if you had something, we would tell…

475
00:53:40.420 --> 00:53:41.110
Justin Florentine (Besu): I mean, the crypto.

476
00:53:41.110 --> 00:53:45.289
Gottfried Herold: team would basically tell you and actually design something.

477
00:53:45.690 --> 00:53:46.360
Justin Florentine (Besu): Okay.

478
00:53:46.610 --> 00:53:47.110
Justin Florentine (Besu): is…

