00:53:47.110 --> 00:54:01.959
Gottfried Herold: We are monitoring this, not for Lucid, for one thing, and we are actually also working on things related to this question, and I mean, good enough threshold scheme would, in fact, be extremely useful for Ethereum, not just for encrypted members.

